text: Norman van de Vater (born 27 August 1946) is an Irish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Irish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:People from Rhondda Cynon Taf
